# Spec-kit runtime state (tooling state — not project artefacts)
# but keep .specify/memory/constitution.md (versioned project artefact, #107)
.specify/memory/*
!.specify/memory/constitution.md

# Local overrides
*.local

# Skeleton skills installed locally for spec workflow (managed externally)
.claude/skills/

# Generated output artefacts (figures, debug PNGs, .npy dumps)
# Tests generate output files; tracked artefacts live in docs/gallery/
tests/output/
output/

# Gallery assets (committed demo/media from docs/gallery/) are tracked
!docs/gallery/

# Rust build artifacts
src/chilmesh_core/target/

# C++ build artifacts
src/chilmesh_cpp/build/
src/chilmesh_cpp/build_local/

# Symlink to /workspace/CHILmesh created by the remote-exec harness at session
# start (points outside the repo) — never track it.
/CHILmesh

# DomI-owned governance artifacts — must NOT live in this consumer repo.
# Introspection corpus is DomI-owned (introspect-v2, DomI #296): records belong in
# DomI .introspect/<repo>/, never here. The deprecated docs/introspections/ path is a
# stale routine-doc directive (DomI claude_routine_instructions.md drift vs the v2 skill);
# guard prevents a session that follows it from re-leaking retros into CHILmesh (#214).
docs/introspections/
.introspect/
.planning/introspections/
